name: title
Kononenko 12mm beam MTCKF 52 wks: Kinematic of 52-week-old MTCKF mice walking on a 12 mm wide beam

name: description
Kononenko 12mm beam MTCKF 52 wks: Original SIMI videos, DeepLabCut-tracked videos and csv files of body kinematics of 52-week-old AP2a1_em knockout mice walking on a wide 12 mm beam. Mixed group of control and mutant mice. Individual trials for each mouse are recorded from 8 cameras and metadata for synchronization is stored as *.smp files.
